	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is indeed a real item.  Praetorian Legion looted this one most recently early in September.  The graphic is that of a red heart (not the symbol, the real thing with arteries etc.) used for several other items in the game as is typical of eq.  Stats are STR 1, DEX 2, STA 1, CHA -10, WIS 2, INT 20 (yes!  twenty int!), AGI 3, Sv F,D,C,P,M  +5.  The effect is Regeneration, which is a great help for necros when in lich form, though the rate is modest at only 5hp per tick.  Still, as a necro myself I think I would take this over the epic weapon.  Stats aren't very much different, but add the regen effect and in lich form it all adds up to extra mana in the long run.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
